            <pubDate>Sun, 31 May 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
            <description><![CDATA[這是一篇 Docusaurus blog 的範例文章，用來確認 Blog 頁面、文章列表、RSS/Atom feed 與導覽列連結都可以正常運作。]]></description>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div class="uriel-like"><div id="uriel-like"></div></div><p>這是一篇 Docusaurus blog 的範例文章，用來確認 Blog 頁面、文章列表、RSS/Atom feed 與導覽列連結都可以正常運作。</p>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="為什麼使用-yearmonth-目錄">為什麼使用 year/month 目錄<a href="https://www.gtcafe.com/blog/2026/05/31/welcome#%E7%82%BA%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BC%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8-yearmonth-%E7%9B%AE%E9%8C%84" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to 為什麼使用 year/month 目錄" title="Direct link to 為什麼使用 year/month 目錄" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<p>Blog 文章可以用時間當目錄結構管理，例如：</p>
<div class="language-text codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_QJqH"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-text codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><div class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">blog/</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">  2026/</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">    05/</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">      welcome.md</span><br></div></code></pre></div></div>
<p>因為檔名不再包含日期，所以文章 front matter 裡要放 <code>date</code>，讓 Docusaurus 可以正確排序與產生文章 metadata。</p>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="url-pattern">URL pattern<a href="https://www.gtcafe.com/blog/2026/05/31/welcome#url-pattern" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to URL pattern" title="Direct link to URL pattern" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<p>Blog 文章網址由 front matter 的 <code>slug</code> 決定。若要使用 <code>/blog/yyyy/mm/dd/title</code>，可以這樣寫：</p>
<div class="language-yaml codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_QJqH"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-yaml codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><div class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token key atrule" style="color:#00a4db">slug</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">:</span><span class="token plain"> 2026/05/31/welcome</span><br></div></code></pre></div></div>
<p>這篇文章的網址會是：</p>
<div class="language-text codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_QJqH"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-text codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><div class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">/blog/2026/05/31/welcome</span><br></div></code></pre></div></div>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="cover-image-與社群-preview">Cover image 與社群 preview<a href="https://www.gtcafe.com/blog/2026/05/31/welcome#cover-image-%E8%88%87%E7%A4%BE%E7%BE%A4-preview" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Cover image 與社群 preview" title="Direct link to Cover image 與社群 preview" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<p>如果要讓文章分享到社群網站時有 preview 圖，在 front matter 裡加上 <code>image</code>：</p>
<div class="language-yaml codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_QJqH"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-yaml codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><div class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token key atrule" style="color:#00a4db">image</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">:</span><span class="token plain"> ./cover</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">-</span><span class="token plain">image.jpg</span><br></div></code></pre></div></div>
<p>Cover 圖可以跟文章放在同一層：</p>
<div class="language-text codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_QJqH"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-text codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><div class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">blog/</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">  2026/</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">    05/</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">      welcome.md</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">      cover-image.jpg</span><br></div></code></pre></div></div>
<p>建議使用 JPG 或 PNG，尺寸用 1200x630，這是 Open Graph preview 最常見的比例。</p>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="圖片放法">圖片放法<a href="https://www.gtcafe.com/blog/2026/05/31/welcome#%E5%9C%96%E7%89%87%E6%94%BE%E6%B3%95" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to 圖片放法" title="Direct link to 圖片放法" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<p>文章用到的圖片可以跟 Markdown 放在同一層，然後用相對路徑引用：</p>
<div class="language-text codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_QJqH"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-text codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><div class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">blog/</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">  2026/</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">    05/</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">      welcome.md</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">      sample-image.svg</span><br></div></code></pre></div></div>
<div class="language-md codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_QJqH"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-md codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><div class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token url operator" style="color:#393A34">!</span><span class="token url" style="color:#36acaa">[</span><span class="token url content" style="color:#36acaa">Blog 範例圖片</span><span class="token url" style="color:#36acaa">](</span><span class="token url" style="color:#36acaa">./sample-image.svg</span><span class="token url" style="color:#36acaa">)</span><br></div></code></pre></div></div>
<p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" alt="Blog 範例圖片" src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," width="1200" height="630" class="img_ev3q"></p>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="下一步">下一步<a href="https://www.gtcafe.com/blog/2026/05/31/welcome#%E4%B8%8B%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A5" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to 下一步" title="Direct link to 下一步" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<p>你可以複製這個檔案到新的年月目錄，改掉 <code>date</code>、<code>slug</code>、<code>title</code>，然後開始撰寫正式文章。</p><section class="uriel-comments"><h2>Comments</h2><div id="uriel-comment"></div></section>]]></content:encoded>
